    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so you think it's mostly just nutrition? it feels like the nutrients are just being sucked out of the plant really fast though. is there any specific way to tell if something is actively stealing the nutrients from the soil or if it's just a slow deficiency?",
